Calendar Clock displays the time of day and time (analogue or digital) and also shows important agenda items, reminders and/or personal messages.
Caretakers (professionals, relatives or friends) can schedule, edit and delete messages, reminders or personal messages. 

To keep the Calendar Clock as easy as possible and also individually usable, an application for administrators has been developed. If the Calendar Clock Administrator app is installed, messages can also be posted remotely after linking with the Calendar Clock. From this administrator application it is also possible to change the appearance of the Calendar Clock application. 

The use of Calendar Clock is also possible without using the Calendar Clock Administrator application.
This application:
• Is FREE;
• Works immediately after installation; 
• Can be used on almost all devices, large and small, new and old;
• Is designed for people with memory impairment or reduced sense of time;
• Stays on continuously;
• Can work without an internet connection; 
• Has a customisable colour scheme; 
• Has a menu screen that can be disabled; 
• Can work in full-screen mode; 
• Can show the current temperature/weather in a city of choice;
• Can show several photos next to the clock;
• Supports alarms and reading confirmations;  
• Can play clock chimes;  
• Is available in Dutch, German, Bulgarian, Indonesian, French, Finnish, Danish, Turkish, Spanish, Italian, Slovenian, and English;
• The colour scheme is customizable;
• Has clear and large letters;
• Is user-friendly due to a minimalist design;
• Can be linked to multiple administrator apps, available under the name “Calendar Clock Administrator”.

Privacy and data processing
The app allows you to save calendar items and personal messages and settings on the Calendar Clock system via a secure connection. This data is only accessible to people with your permission. Calendar Clock stores this data only so that it can be changed by the administrator(s) . We do not process or analyse this data and it can also be deleted at any time upon request. For more information on this, see our Privacy Policy or contact us.
